    "body": "This case invokes bitcoin-cli via raw subprocess.run() without -datadir, so it reads the default datadir's bitcoin.conf (e.g. ~/.bitcoin) and fails whenever that real config is unusable. Pass the node's -datadir so the check reads the test's own bitcoin.conf and depends only on the build's IPC support, not the host environment.",
